sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant BumpScript as bump-version.sh
    participant ReleaseScript as generate-release-notes.sh
    participant Converter as scripts/converter.py
    participant Git as Git Repository
    participant GHA as GitHub Actions
    participant Marketplace as Claude Marketplace
    
    Dev->>BumpScript: ./bump-version.sh 3.2.0
    BumpScript->>Git: Update 11 version files
    BumpScript->>Git: Commit + tag v3.2.0
    
    Dev->>ReleaseScript: ./generate-release-notes.sh
    ReleaseScript->>Git: Parse git log since last tag
    ReleaseScript->>ReleaseScript: Categorize commits<br/>(Added/Changed/Fixed)
    ReleaseScript->>Git: Output release-notes.md
    
    Dev->>Converter: python scripts/converter.py
    Converter->>Git: Generate Codex markdown
    Converter->>Git: Generate Gemini TOML
    Converter->>Git: Generate OpenCode markdown
    
    Dev->>Git: git push --tags
    Git->>GHA: Trigger on tag push
    GHA->>GHA: Read release-notes.md
    GHA->>Git: Create GitHub Release
    
    Note over Marketplace: Plugin updates are<br/>automatic via marketplace
